(i) the collection, use and disclosure by the XYZ Institutions of your personal information, including your personal health information for the purposes of: (a) institutional planning to assist with the creation (b) notification and/or delivery of other programs and services (c) statistical analysis necessary to further assist  (d) planning of or response to a natural disaster or other event deemed to be an emergency (collectively, the "Purposes"); and (ii) being contacted by the XYZ Institutions for reasons related to the Purposes. For more information please review our<%= link_to "Â https://ge-stage-2019.herokuapp.com/privacy_policy", home_new_path%> *<strong>
  </label>
</div>
<div>
    <%# <%= content_tag :div, class: 'js-dependent-fields', data: { 'checkbox-id': 'user_extended_profile', 'checkbox-value': 'true'} %> 
  <%= f.radio_button :terms, true %> I Agree<br /> 
</div>

<div>
  <%= f.radio_button :terms, false %> I Do not Agree<br />
  <%= content_tag :div, class: 'js-dependent-fields', data: { 'radio-name': 'user[terms]', 'radio-value': 'false' } do %>
    <strong> contact Admin at <%= mail_to "xyz@projectname.com "%><strong>
  <% end %>
</div>

  <div class="actions">
    <%= f.submit "Sign up" %>
  </div>
<% end %>

